WEBVTT

00:01:15.700 --> 00:01:20.940
=About Love=

00:01:21.000 --> 00:01:23.940
=Episode 16=

00:01:41.870 --> 00:01:43.480
Haven't been here for ages, huh?

00:01:45.150 --> 00:01:46.760
Feels like everything's changed.

00:01:47.710 --> 00:01:49.510
Nah, this bridge looks just the same.

00:01:55.870 --> 00:01:57.120
Being with me,

00:01:58.210 --> 00:01:59.230
have you ever been happy?

00:02:01.230 --> 00:02:02.070
What about you?

00:02:02.280 --> 00:02:03.310
I'm asking you.

00:02:03.680 --> 00:02:05.040
Of course I have.

00:02:07.840 --> 00:02:08.680
Yu,

00:02:09.190 --> 00:02:10.360
I'll make you even happier.

00:02:14.080 --> 00:02:16.680
I remember
the bar's just behind there, right?

00:02:17.030 --> 00:02:17.870
Yeah.

00:02:18.900 --> 00:02:26.340
(Qinglong Bridge)

00:02:54.840 --> 00:02:55.870
What made you come here?

00:02:56.280 --> 00:02:57.190
Is it bad?

00:02:57.190 --> 00:02:58.030
No,

00:02:58.560 --> 00:02:59.400
it's good.

00:02:59.560 --> 00:03:00.840
Just a bit far.

00:03:03.280 --> 00:03:04.280
Yeah.

00:03:08.470 --> 00:03:09.470
Feeling more relaxed?

00:03:10.840 --> 00:03:11.870
I mean,

00:03:11.870 --> 00:03:13.520
finally free from
your mom's supervision.

00:03:14.910 --> 00:03:15.870
You noticed?

00:03:16.190 --> 00:03:17.150
Well, elders

00:03:18.080 --> 00:03:19.240
do get a bit anxious.

00:03:19.910 --> 00:03:20.750
But it's fine.

00:03:20.860 --> 00:03:21.870
Don't let it bother you.

00:03:22.280 --> 00:03:23.910
We can go at our own pace.

00:03:24.470 --> 00:03:26.030
I don't want every time we meet

00:03:26.560 --> 00:03:28.000
to be for you to finish a task.

00:03:33.870 --> 00:03:35.120
We're still friends, right?

00:03:36.280 --> 00:03:37.120
Of course.

00:03:38.680 --> 00:03:41.590
I'm fine with you, mostly my mom.

00:03:41.590 --> 00:03:42.590
I know.

00:03:43.400 --> 00:03:44.240
It's okay.

00:03:45.590 --> 00:03:46.750
Don't pressure yourself.

00:03:48.800 --> 00:03:50.150
We can be like before.

00:03:53.870 --> 00:03:55.560
Next up,

00:03:56.000 --> 00:03:57.190
the song is called Unicorn.

00:03:58.280 --> 00:03:59.240
The unicorn stands for

00:03:59.240 --> 00:04:00.750
unwavering devotion in love.

00:04:01.590 --> 00:04:03.590
I want to tell the girl
I like in the audience

00:04:04.600 --> 00:04:05.800
that I'll keep waiting for her.

00:04:06.750 --> 00:04:08.000
Until she gives me an answer.

00:04:17.820 --> 00:04:21.790
♪In the story of love, there are many♪

00:04:21.790 --> 00:04:24.620
♪Different twists and turns♪

00:04:25.780 --> 00:04:29.280
♪You're my little joy♪

00:04:29.280 --> 00:04:33.150
♪So precious and beautiful in my heart♪

00:04:33.810 --> 00:04:37.050
♪Is all about us you and me♪

00:04:37.050 --> 00:04:41.310
♪I love getting lost in this feeling♪

00:04:41.800 --> 00:04:45.450
♪You and me, in your eyes♪

00:04:45.570 --> 00:04:48.870
♪I search for my reflection♪

00:04:53.950 --> 00:04:54.950
Do you still remember?

00:04:55.700 --> 00:04:57.510
Back then,
you were standing right there too.

00:04:59.430 --> 00:05:01.430
I do. Feels so childish looking back.

00:05:05.480 --> 00:05:06.390
Childish?

00:05:09.620 --> 00:05:13.140
♪All this belongs only to us two♪

00:05:13.780 --> 00:05:19.760
♪You're my cherished unicorn♪

00:05:21.480 --> 00:05:22.920
You like this band?

00:05:23.360 --> 00:05:24.310
Yeah.

00:05:26.190 --> 00:05:27.390
But not that much.

00:05:30.480 --> 00:05:31.720
So do you like it

00:05:31.720 --> 00:05:32.750
or not?

00:05:36.830 --> 00:05:37.950
I guess I do like it.

00:05:41.810 --> 00:05:44.070
♪On the map of love♪

00:05:44.070 --> 00:05:48.870
♪Footprints run deep and light♪

00:05:49.190 --> 00:05:50.510
What kind of band is this?

00:05:50.830 --> 00:05:52.950
It makes you overthink
just saying "I like it."

00:05:54.120 --> 00:05:55.390
You noticed I was overthinking?

00:05:56.270 --> 00:05:57.390
That's not what I meant.

00:05:57.760 --> 00:06:01.030
♪Is all about us you and me♪

00:06:01.030 --> 00:06:02.820
♪Wrapped in sweetness and care♪

00:06:04.000 --> 00:06:04.920
You know him?

00:06:05.790 --> 00:06:09.120
♪You and me, in our hearts♪

00:06:09.750 --> 00:06:10.750
You came here

00:06:11.870 --> 00:06:12.830
for him?

00:06:16.360 --> 00:06:17.240
It's okay.

00:06:18.390 --> 00:06:19.240
Don't push yourself.

00:06:21.310 --> 00:06:22.720
Stay or leave.

00:06:24.070 --> 00:06:25.160
I'll be with you.

00:06:27.240 --> 00:06:28.080
Thank you.

00:06:39.830 --> 00:06:40.680
Thanks.

00:07:02.240 --> 00:07:03.630
Why are we running?

00:07:03.830 --> 00:07:05.040
I'm gonna jump. Don't stop me.

00:07:05.720 --> 00:07:07.040
Are you crazy?

00:07:08.680 --> 00:07:10.270
You came all this way.

00:07:10.270 --> 00:07:11.950
Why leave now?

00:07:11.950 --> 00:07:12.800
If you go with him,

00:07:12.800 --> 00:07:14.190
where will I find you?

00:07:15.070 --> 00:07:16.600
He didn't kidnap me.

00:07:17.750 --> 00:07:19.360
Where have you been lately?

00:07:19.630 --> 00:07:21.070
With that guy the whole time?

00:07:23.430 --> 00:07:24.830
I've been thinking

00:07:25.510 --> 00:07:26.630
whether I'll say yes to you.

00:07:28.830 --> 00:07:30.390
You didn't answer my calls.

00:07:32.190 --> 00:07:33.750
I was afraid

00:07:34.560 --> 00:07:35.800
I'd say yes right away.

00:07:37.830 --> 00:07:39.800
You still haven't decided
if you wanna be with me?

00:07:42.430 --> 00:07:43.800
Did you even court me?

00:07:44.600 --> 00:07:46.040
You never courted me.

00:07:46.160 --> 00:07:47.240
What's there to think about?

00:07:47.430 --> 00:07:48.870
What do I need to do to court you?

00:07:49.750 --> 00:07:50.800
Make me happy.

00:07:51.800 --> 00:07:53.870
I just want someone who makes me happy.

00:08:02.120 --> 00:08:03.190
A clown?

00:08:03.190 --> 00:08:04.030
I'll take a photo for you.

00:08:06.630 --> 00:08:09.600
Three, two, one, cheese!

00:08:16.630 --> 00:08:17.680
Let's sit for a bit.

00:08:23.830 --> 00:08:24.670
Iced milk tea?

00:08:25.800 --> 00:08:27.390
I don't drink cold drinks anymore.

00:08:30.070 --> 00:08:31.480
Two milk teas. One iced, one hot.

00:08:31.480 --> 00:08:32.360
Okay.

00:08:32.360 --> 00:08:34.240
(Iced Jelly &amp; Iced Tangyuan)

00:08:34.240 --> 00:08:36.000
Can I get a hot tea instead? Thanks.

00:08:36.000 --> 00:08:36.840
Got it.

00:08:37.720 --> 00:08:39.120
Why didn't you buy two?

00:08:40.150 --> 00:08:41.240
A bit short on cash.

00:08:42.390 --> 00:08:43.510
I'll treat you.

00:08:44.240 --> 00:08:45.670
This is so childish.

00:08:45.670 --> 00:08:47.910
Perfect for you. Super youthful.

00:08:55.410 --> 00:08:56.270
Tea's here.

00:08:56.270 --> 00:08:57.630
- Thank you.
- Thank you.

00:08:57.790 --> 00:08:58.630
Here, this is yours.

00:08:59.390 --> 00:09:00.230
Please enjoy.

00:09:16.080 --> 00:09:17.320
You care about me a lot?

00:09:17.510 --> 00:09:18.350
No.

00:09:21.360 --> 00:09:23.600
Well, if I give up now,

00:09:23.790 --> 00:09:25.270
would it be too soon or too late?

00:09:25.510 --> 00:09:27.630
What if one day
you can't stand me anymore?

00:09:28.550 --> 00:09:29.750
Since I love you,

00:09:31.120 --> 00:09:32.200
I won't regret it.

00:09:32.550 --> 00:09:33.750
So confident, huh?

00:09:34.240 --> 00:09:35.440
I trust myself.

00:09:36.150 --> 00:09:37.630
We're similar in that way.

00:09:38.870 --> 00:09:39.790
Come on.

00:09:40.320 --> 00:09:42.240
You don't even have a solid reason.

00:09:42.240 --> 00:09:43.390
Yet I still choose to trust you.

00:09:43.630 --> 00:09:44.630
Because I love you.

00:09:45.080 --> 00:09:46.200
But you don't believe me.

00:09:46.290 --> 00:09:47.150
What does that mean?

00:09:47.150 --> 00:09:50.200
It means I love you
way more than you love me.

00:09:52.150 --> 00:09:54.440
I don't trust you
but still choose to love you.

00:09:55.270 --> 00:09:56.440
So technically,

00:09:57.150 --> 00:09:58.240
I might love you more.

00:09:58.240 --> 00:09:59.960
Fair enough. I'll take it.

00:10:00.750 --> 00:10:02.080
You're messing with me!

00:10:06.480 --> 00:10:07.510
(Maybe being in love)

00:10:07.670 --> 00:10:08.910
(makes people reckless.)

00:10:09.960 --> 00:10:10.960
(And makes us believe)

00:10:10.960 --> 00:10:12.510
(we have the courage and ability)

00:10:12.870 --> 00:10:14.630
(to face every challenge ahead.)

00:10:21.750 --> 00:10:22.840
Sir, add some cold water.

00:10:23.080 --> 00:10:24.000
Got it.

00:10:30.910 --> 00:10:31.750
Enjoy your drink.

00:10:37.080 --> 00:10:38.000
Here's your key.

00:10:38.270 --> 00:10:40.240
Go out, turn right, first room upstairs.

00:10:40.240 --> 00:10:41.240
Have a nice stay.

00:10:41.240 --> 00:10:42.550
- Okay, thanks.
- Thanks.

00:10:44.840 --> 00:10:45.680
On the right.

00:10:48.120 --> 00:10:49.550
It's so beautiful here.

00:10:49.910 --> 00:10:51.080
The air is fresh.

00:10:51.440 --> 00:10:52.910
Like a natural oxygen bar.

00:10:53.200 --> 00:10:54.630
So comfortable.

00:10:55.100 --> 00:10:57.390
I was worried I'd pick the wrong spot
and you wouldn't like it.

00:10:57.600 --> 00:10:58.720
How could I not like it?

00:10:59.390 --> 00:11:01.080
Everything you choose is perfect.

00:11:06.550 --> 00:11:08.080
There's even a terrace here.

00:11:09.720 --> 00:11:12.030
Look, the scenery
over there is stunning.

00:11:13.360 --> 00:11:14.390
It really is beautiful.

00:11:16.240 --> 00:11:17.240
Are you talking about me?

00:11:17.720 --> 00:11:19.030
Who else would I be talking about?

00:11:20.720 --> 00:11:22.120
You're even prettier than the view.

00:11:22.120 --> 00:11:23.000
Look over there.

00:11:23.000 --> 00:11:23.870
So pretty too.

00:11:24.320 --> 00:11:25.750
No view is more beautiful than you.

00:11:31.600 --> 00:11:33.320
Do you ever think things through?

00:11:34.790 --> 00:11:36.600
Why are you so reckless?

00:11:38.080 --> 00:11:39.840
You really don't make things
easy for me.

00:11:39.840 --> 00:11:42.150
Living with you is so tiring.

00:11:42.150 --> 00:11:44.120
No, I just didn't think of that.

00:11:44.130 --> 00:11:45.550
Why didn't you ask when booking?

00:11:45.840 --> 00:11:47.120
Didn't even check if there's AC?

00:11:47.120 --> 00:11:48.510
I thought AC was standard.

00:11:48.510 --> 00:11:50.120
How could I know they didn't have it?

00:11:50.120 --> 00:11:51.960
Thought this and that.
Everything's just what you think.

00:11:52.360 --> 00:11:54.150
Does the world revolve around you?

00:11:54.320 --> 00:11:55.320
And we stayed at

00:11:55.320 --> 00:11:56.270
this same homestay last time.

00:11:56.270 --> 00:11:57.720
It didn't have AC either.

00:11:57.720 --> 00:11:59.240
Dude, what season was it last time?

00:11:59.240 --> 00:12:00.840
And what season is it now?

00:12:02.480 --> 00:12:03.750
Are you really this stupid,

00:12:03.750 --> 00:12:05.030
or just pretending?

00:12:08.120 --> 00:12:10.150
Go ask how to fix this!

00:12:15.750 --> 00:12:16.720
Unbelievable.

00:12:24.030 --> 00:12:25.000
What did the front desk say?

00:12:27.000 --> 00:12:28.000
They said

00:12:28.480 --> 00:12:30.200
it says "no AC" on the booking page.

00:12:30.200 --> 00:12:31.120
They're not responsible.

00:12:32.270 --> 00:12:33.550
So they're calling you blind.

00:12:33.870 --> 00:12:34.840
And then?

00:12:35.480 --> 00:12:36.630
No refunds, of course.

00:12:36.640 --> 00:12:38.390
We can only find someone else
to take the room.

00:12:38.840 --> 00:12:39.910
Pack up. Let's leave.

00:12:40.670 --> 00:12:41.670
Where are you going?

00:12:41.670 --> 00:12:43.150
They're treating you like a fool.

00:12:43.150 --> 00:12:44.240
And you wanna stay?

00:12:44.580 --> 00:12:45.440
It's so late.

00:12:45.440 --> 00:12:46.870
All this over AC?

00:12:46.870 --> 00:12:47.840
Yes, I'm picky.

00:12:47.840 --> 00:12:48.740
I don't settle.

00:12:48.740 --> 00:12:50.780
(Hotel)

00:12:51.720 --> 00:12:52.870
Pack up.

00:14:03.000 --> 00:14:04.120
You smell nice today.

00:14:05.360 --> 00:14:06.320
Stop it.

00:14:29.390 --> 00:14:30.360
What's wrong?

00:14:31.910 --> 00:14:32.910
I didn't bring that.

00:14:34.600 --> 00:14:35.870
It should be fine.

00:14:36.630 --> 00:14:38.670
No, safety comes first.

00:14:40.440 --> 00:14:41.480
Good boy.

00:14:42.750 --> 00:14:44.080
Wait here, I'll go buy it.

00:14:45.360 --> 00:14:46.200
Hey.

00:14:46.960 --> 00:14:47.840
Let me go get it.

00:14:48.080 --> 00:14:49.600
I can grab some snacks too.

00:14:50.510 --> 00:14:51.350
Can you handle it?

00:14:51.720 --> 00:14:52.750
Of course.

00:14:53.550 --> 00:14:54.510
Just wait here for me.

00:14:55.080 --> 00:14:56.270
Call me if anything happens.

00:14:56.270 --> 00:14:57.200
Nothing will.

00:15:10.630 --> 00:15:11.630
Forgot to tell you.

00:15:12.440 --> 00:15:13.390
You're super handsome.

00:15:48.390 --> 00:15:49.510
Where is it?

00:15:52.480 --> 00:15:53.320
Xiu.

00:15:54.390 --> 00:15:55.230
Xiu.

00:15:56.120 --> 00:15:56.960
What's wrong?

00:15:56.960 --> 00:15:58.320
Did you see my serum?

00:15:58.630 --> 00:15:59.510
What serum?

00:15:59.510 --> 00:16:01.360
The purple bottle. I use it every day.

00:16:01.750 --> 00:16:02.600
Did you bring it?

00:16:02.870 --> 00:16:05.000
Yeah, I took it out at the inn.

00:16:06.080 --> 00:16:07.790
Did you pack it when we left?

00:16:08.440 --> 00:16:09.510
I thought you'd

00:16:09.510 --> 00:16:10.480
pack your own stuff.

00:16:10.480 --> 00:16:11.720
What do you mean "you thought"?

00:16:11.720 --> 00:16:13.480
Can't you help pack my things too?

00:16:13.480 --> 00:16:15.080
That's not what I meant, really.

00:16:15.270 --> 00:16:16.960
It must be at the inn. Go get it for me.

00:16:18.150 --> 00:16:19.240
Is it expensive?

00:16:19.240 --> 00:16:20.910
Over ten thousand a bottle,
what do you think?

00:16:22.150 --> 00:16:23.550
I use it every day.

00:16:24.080 --> 00:16:25.270
I'm not young anymore.

00:16:25.440 --> 00:16:26.550
I'll deserve you even less

00:16:26.550 --> 00:16:27.390
if I stop using them.

00:16:27.630 --> 00:16:28.910
Fine, I'll go get it.

00:16:37.670 --> 00:16:38.510
Hello.

00:16:39.080 --> 00:16:40.080
May I ask

00:16:40.260 --> 00:16:41.200
if you cleaned the room

00:16:41.200 --> 00:16:42.040
we were in earlier?

00:16:42.200 --> 00:16:43.240
Yes.

00:16:43.510 --> 00:16:44.720
Did you get a bottle of

00:16:44.720 --> 00:16:45.840
purple serum bottle?

00:16:46.360 --> 00:16:47.790
No.

00:16:48.960 --> 00:16:50.240
Can I go check?

00:16:50.600 --> 00:16:52.150
Sir, we inspect the room thoroughly

00:16:52.150 --> 00:16:53.320
after checkout.

00:16:53.360 --> 00:16:54.200
There really isn't one.

00:16:54.200 --> 00:16:55.240
Okay, I know.

00:16:55.240 --> 00:16:56.200
But I just wanna see.

00:17:07.920 --> 00:17:09.110
It truly wasn't there.

00:17:10.250 --> 00:17:11.510
Maybe it got tossed out as trash?

00:17:11.510 --> 00:17:12.350
Where's the trash bin?

00:17:12.830 --> 00:17:13.670
It's outside.

00:17:29.710 --> 00:17:33.770
♪Holding my breath
to face the lonely sea♪

00:17:34.560 --> 00:17:37.110
♪The surroundings are no longer blue♪

00:17:37.580 --> 00:17:40.640
♪The warmth around me is gone♪

00:17:41.680 --> 00:17:46.050
♪Longing for a sigh to blow away
the dust in my heart♪

00:17:46.470 --> 00:17:49.100
♪Thoughts no longer linger♪

00:17:49.370 --> 00:17:52.680
♪Heartbeat no longer slow♪

00:17:54.090 --> 00:17:57.030
♪In loneliness, I bear♪

00:17:57.610 --> 00:18:00.460
♪The world's wounds♪

00:18:00.680 --> 00:18:03.840
♪The haze within my heart♪

00:18:06.080 --> 00:18:09.130
♪Lost in loneliness♪

00:18:09.650 --> 00:18:12.220
♪The world closing in♪

00:18:12.770 --> 00:18:15.460
♪No light can reach inside♪

00:18:16.870 --> 00:18:18.690
♪I favor love♪

00:18:18.690 --> 00:18:21.220
♪And I reflect on it♪

00:18:21.790 --> 00:18:24.350
♪Let black and white stand side by side♪

00:18:24.830 --> 00:18:26.550
(Yu, I'm sorry.)

00:18:27.750 --> 00:18:28.590
(I can't find it.)

00:18:29.480 --> 00:18:30.790
(I really tried my best.)

00:18:31.640 --> 00:18:32.880
(But I can't get it back.)

00:18:33.780 --> 00:18:36.250
♪Time reveals♪

00:18:36.690 --> 00:18:40.440
♪Then rips the future away♪

00:18:40.880 --> 00:18:44.370
♪I can't explain it♪

00:18:44.370 --> 00:18:45.690
♪Letting go♪

00:18:45.690 --> 00:18:47.190
♪Only makes it harder to bear♪

00:18:47.190 --> 00:18:52.490
♪What I want won't return♪

00:18:52.730 --> 00:18:54.370
♪Some tears♪

00:18:54.370 --> 00:18:56.430
♪I can't shed♪

00:18:56.430 --> 00:18:57.700
♪The deep sea♪

00:18:57.700 --> 00:18:59.270
♪Overgrown with helplessness♪

00:18:59.270 --> 00:19:04.620
♪Overgrown with my sorrow♪

00:19:04.730 --> 00:19:07.320
♪A sudden collapse♪

00:19:07.790 --> 00:19:10.450
♪Happiness is gone♪

00:19:10.450 --> 00:19:12.200
♪Can't force it♪

00:19:12.410 --> 00:19:17.680
♪Can't start over♪

00:19:19.890 --> 00:19:21.730
♪I've been won over by love♪

00:19:21.730 --> 00:19:24.000
♪Then sold by love again♪

00:19:24.750 --> 00:19:27.100
♪Heartlessness ignores me♪

00:19:27.650 --> 00:19:30.930
♪Life feels pure as snow♪

00:19:31.880 --> 00:19:33.750
♪I'm covered in love♪

00:19:33.750 --> 00:19:36.240
♪Then love cast me out♪

00:19:36.790 --> 00:19:39.590
♪Regret keeps giving♪

00:19:39.800 --> 00:19:43.890
♪Extending the story's extra chapter♪

00:19:43.890 --> 00:19:45.570
♪I favor love♪

00:19:45.570 --> 00:19:48.120
♪And I reflect on it♪

00:19:48.630 --> 00:19:51.570
♪Let black and white stand side by side♪

00:19:51.770 --> 00:19:55.050
♪No grey area♪

00:20:02.300 --> 00:20:05.060
(Hua)

00:20:10.640 --> 00:20:11.480
Hello.

00:20:13.270 --> 00:20:15.750
Two black tea cake sets, please.

00:20:16.880 --> 00:20:19.150
Can you replace one cake with a salad?

00:20:19.160 --> 00:20:20.020
Thanks.

00:20:20.030 --> 00:20:21.310
- A salad, right?
- Yeah.

00:20:21.590 --> 00:20:22.720
Better give her the cake.

00:20:23.720 --> 00:20:25.030
Okay, please wait a moment.

00:20:28.160 --> 00:20:29.510
Eating sugar

00:20:29.750 --> 00:20:30.720
helps

00:20:31.440 --> 00:20:33.000
your brain release more dopamine.

00:20:36.110 --> 00:20:37.480
How do you know I'm feeling down?

00:20:38.000 --> 00:20:39.550
If you weren't,

00:20:39.550 --> 00:20:40.750
you'd never agree to

00:20:41.160 --> 00:20:42.480
eat with me.

00:20:46.270 --> 00:20:47.400
Are you on a business trip?

00:20:47.920 --> 00:20:48.910
How long are you staying?

00:20:49.070 --> 00:20:50.070
Leaving tomorrow morning.

00:20:50.750 --> 00:20:51.720
Pretty coincidental, huh?

00:20:53.310 --> 00:20:54.200
Yeah.

00:20:58.550 --> 00:20:59.440
Thanks.

00:20:59.790 --> 00:21:00.630
Thanks.

00:21:09.640 --> 00:21:11.680
I actually need a favor.

00:21:11.920 --> 00:21:12.760
Yeah.

00:21:13.240 --> 00:21:14.480
I have a friend.

00:21:14.790 --> 00:21:15.790
We grew up together.

00:21:16.480 --> 00:21:17.320
She's

00:21:17.720 --> 00:21:19.920
used to keeping everything to herself.

00:21:20.620 --> 00:21:21.480
I can't find

00:21:21.480 --> 00:21:22.830
a good way to comfort her.

00:21:23.160 --> 00:21:24.000
Of course.

00:21:24.200 --> 00:21:25.790
I don't want to
come across as intrusive.

00:21:39.160 --> 00:21:40.000
Delicious?

00:21:41.750 --> 00:21:42.640
Sweet.

00:21:48.270 --> 00:21:49.110
Mm.

00:21:53.400 --> 00:21:54.590
Wanna talk?

00:21:57.830 --> 00:21:58.670
Sure.

00:22:01.640 --> 00:22:02.920
Honestly, I'm not doing so well.

00:22:06.790 --> 00:22:09.310
(Luanluan)
(Still rehearsing tonight, so tired.)

00:22:10.030 --> 00:22:11.440
(Did you have fun with her?)

00:22:11.750 --> 00:22:13.510
(Take good care of her, okay?)

00:22:14.440 --> 00:22:16.350
(Don't be careless again.)

00:22:16.510 --> 00:22:17.750
(Don't make her mad.)

00:22:18.030 --> 00:22:20.000
(Girls need careful care.)

00:22:20.270 --> 00:22:21.680
(You have to coax her, understand?)

00:22:21.900 --> 00:22:22.750
(By the way,)

00:22:22.750 --> 00:22:25.030
(better prepare
a small gift or a surprise.)

00:22:25.350 --> 00:22:27.830
(Like a ring or necklace.)

00:22:27.900 --> 00:22:28.920
(She'll definitely love it.)

00:22:29.440 --> 00:22:31.110
(Hope we're on the same page.)

00:22:31.440 --> 00:22:32.590
(You'll prepare it, right?)

00:22:33.070 --> 00:22:34.160
(Don't let me down.)

00:22:34.310 --> 00:22:35.880
(Most importantly, don't let her down.)

00:22:36.720 --> 00:22:39.030
(No need to rush back for
tomorrow's performance.)

00:22:39.030 --> 00:22:40.110
(They'll all show up,)

00:22:40.160 --> 00:22:41.400
(so it's fine if you don't come.)

00:22:41.720 --> 00:22:43.680
(Just stay and keep her company.)

00:22:44.000 --> 00:22:45.200
(Try to spend a few more days.)

00:22:45.770 --> 00:22:47.860
(She rarely finds time to
hang out with you.)

00:22:47.870 --> 00:22:49.400
(So she truly cares about you
and loves you.)

00:22:50.030 --> 00:22:51.440
(Hope this is a fresh start.)

00:22:51.880 --> 00:22:52.720
(Come on.)

00:22:52.790 --> 00:22:54.870
♪I'll stay insane♪

00:22:55.510 --> 00:22:56.550
(Good night, baby.)

00:22:56.980 --> 00:22:58.700
(Luanluan deleted a message)

00:23:01.840 --> 00:23:06.570
♪You know what I'll say♪

00:23:08.880 --> 00:23:09.870
(Xiu)
(I want to see you)

00:23:12.350 --> 00:23:13.440
Actually, marriage

00:23:14.720 --> 00:23:16.750
is sometimes just a piece of paper.

00:23:18.350 --> 00:23:19.350
Over the years,

00:23:19.720 --> 00:23:20.790
I've fought with my mom

00:23:20.790 --> 00:23:22.350
so many times because of him.

00:23:23.270 --> 00:23:24.480
I remember when he

00:23:25.200 --> 00:23:27.070
used to play the guitar on stage,

00:23:27.640 --> 00:23:29.240
so young, so full of energy.

00:23:29.790 --> 00:23:30.880
Being with him

00:23:31.310 --> 00:23:33.030
made me feel like
I was just a little girl.

00:23:37.440 --> 00:23:38.680
I just don't get it.

00:23:40.750 --> 00:23:42.200
I loved him with everything I had.

00:23:44.110 --> 00:23:46.070
How did it end up like this?

00:23:54.830 --> 00:23:55.880
Sunk cost.

00:23:57.920 --> 00:23:58.830
Actually,

00:23:59.160 --> 00:24:00.030
cutting losses in time

00:24:01.400 --> 00:24:03.160
might turn out to be the wiser choice.

00:24:10.160 --> 00:24:11.270
Have you heard that story?

00:24:12.310 --> 00:24:13.880
If every piece of wood

00:24:14.160 --> 00:24:15.270
on Ship of Theseus

00:24:15.830 --> 00:24:16.750
is replaced,

00:24:17.380 --> 00:24:18.240
is it...

00:24:18.240 --> 00:24:20.240
Still the same ship?

00:24:25.270 --> 00:24:26.440
As long as the river is there,

00:24:27.330 --> 00:24:28.480
no matter how the water flows,

00:24:31.240 --> 00:24:32.510
it's still the same river.

00:24:38.110 --> 00:24:38.960
Another question.

00:24:40.000 --> 00:24:41.350
What if we build a new ship

00:24:42.200 --> 00:24:43.240
with the original wood?

00:24:46.300 --> 00:24:47.440
There's no original wood left.

00:24:47.450 --> 00:24:52.530
♪I lie awake♪

00:24:52.810 --> 00:24:56.720
♪Thinking bout how to stay the same♪

00:24:59.160 --> 00:25:00.000
My treat.

00:25:00.400 --> 00:25:01.550
You asked me out, after all.

00:25:01.550 --> 00:25:08.410
♪I lie awake all night,♪

00:25:09.880 --> 00:25:10.720
Ah.

00:25:10.920 --> 00:25:12.030
I'm here. No need to walk me in.

00:25:12.800 --> 00:25:14.400
♪Only to lie♪

00:25:15.310 --> 00:25:16.150
I live here.

00:25:20.030 --> 00:25:21.000
That's quite a coincidence.

00:25:22.680 --> 00:25:24.390
Goodnight.

00:25:25.590 --> 00:25:26.510
Sleep well.

00:25:35.640 --> 00:25:36.510
(Where are you?)

00:25:43.780 --> 00:25:44.620
(Xiu)

00:25:50.790 --> 00:25:52.070
Hey, where are you?

00:25:52.240 --> 00:25:54.110
Hey, hey, hey!

00:25:54.160 --> 00:25:55.440
Are you a friend of the phone owner?

00:25:56.590 --> 00:25:58.440
I… I am. Who's speaking?

00:25:59.550 --> 00:26:00.510
Someone fell into the water.

00:26:00.790 --> 00:26:02.480
I'm watching his phone. Don't worry.

00:26:03.510 --> 00:26:04.680
Fell into the water?

00:26:05.510 --> 00:26:07.480
Where… where are you exactly?

00:26:14.750 --> 00:26:15.590
Hua.

00:26:15.590 --> 00:26:16.550
Can you drive for me?

00:26:20.000 --> 00:26:22.000
Take it easy, we'll be there soon.

00:26:31.200 --> 00:26:33.210
- All good? Did something fall?
- Excuse me, sorry.

00:26:33.210 --> 00:26:34.070
Sorry, sorry.

00:26:34.070 --> 00:26:35.000
Excuse me, sorry.

00:26:35.000 --> 00:26:36.240
Hello, please cooperate with us.

00:26:36.240 --> 00:26:37.080
Keep back, please.

00:26:37.080 --> 00:26:38.310
Officer, we're his family.

00:26:39.030 --> 00:26:39.880
- Family?
- Yeah.

00:26:40.030 --> 00:26:40.960
Alright, come on in.

00:26:41.920 --> 00:26:43.110
What happened? Why so reckless?

00:26:43.110 --> 00:26:44.720
Lucky that guy showed up.
Could've been bad.

00:26:44.720 --> 00:26:45.920
- Where is he?
- Here.

00:26:45.920 --> 00:26:46.760
Here.

00:26:49.830 --> 00:26:51.070
This is a woman?

00:26:51.550 --> 00:26:52.720
We're the man's family.

00:26:53.030 --> 00:26:53.880
- The man?
- Ah.

00:26:54.790 --> 00:26:55.680
He's in that car.

00:26:55.680 --> 00:26:57.110
We need to
take a quick statement from him.

00:26:57.920 --> 00:26:58.880
Hey,

00:26:58.880 --> 00:26:59.880
slow down, Yu.

00:26:59.940 --> 00:27:00.790
Take it easy.

00:27:00.790 --> 00:27:01.750
I'll call you later.

00:27:01.750 --> 00:27:02.590
Xiu,

00:27:04.480 --> 00:27:05.910
- you okay?
- I'm fine.

00:27:06.550 --> 00:27:08.590
- Xiu, I'm sorry.
- It's fine. It's fine.

00:27:08.590 --> 00:27:09.790
I'm sorry. It's all my fault.

00:27:09.790 --> 00:27:10.640
- It's fine.
- My bad.

00:27:10.640 --> 00:27:11.590
Sorry for snapping.

00:27:11.590 --> 00:27:13.080
- My bad.
- I'm sorry.

00:27:13.140 --> 00:27:14.000
My bad, my bad.

00:27:14.000 --> 00:27:14.920
I was terrified.

00:27:14.920 --> 00:27:16.070
- My bad.
- I thought you...

00:27:16.070 --> 00:27:17.560
- Alright, alright.
- The wind's picking up.

00:27:18.110 --> 00:27:18.960
Don't catch a cold.

00:27:20.070 --> 00:27:21.070
I'll drive you two back.

00:27:30.920 --> 00:27:31.960
By the way, dear.

00:27:33.750 --> 00:27:34.590
What's wrong?

00:27:40.070 --> 00:27:41.030
Lucky.

00:27:41.480 --> 00:27:42.590
Almost lost it.

00:27:42.920 --> 00:27:43.760
Dear.

00:27:45.240 --> 00:27:46.550
When we got married,

00:27:49.200 --> 00:27:50.680
I couldn't even get you a ring.

00:27:53.350 --> 00:27:54.750
I wanna tell you

00:27:56.790 --> 00:27:58.350
those songs of mine are getting popular.

00:27:59.590 --> 00:28:00.750
I'm making money now.

00:28:07.830 --> 00:28:09.160
So today, I'm making it up to you.

00:28:13.590 --> 00:28:14.440
Also,

00:28:15.070 --> 00:28:16.510
I'm about to sign with a new company.

00:28:17.440 --> 00:28:19.480
That big house with a garden you wanted.

00:28:21.030 --> 00:28:22.070
I'll work for it.

00:28:24.640 --> 00:28:26.440
Give me another chance, okay?

00:28:32.310 --> 00:28:34.400
I never wanted a big house.

00:28:36.880 --> 00:28:38.000
I just wanted you.

00:28:40.440 --> 00:28:42.200
When I heard you
fell into the water, I...

00:28:42.590 --> 00:28:43.920
I was terrified.

00:28:46.720 --> 00:28:48.270
I just want you to be safe.

00:28:49.830 --> 00:28:51.310
Always by my side.

00:28:52.550 --> 00:28:53.440
I understand.

00:28:55.160 --> 00:28:56.110
I know.

00:28:57.480 --> 00:28:58.590
Don't leave me.

00:29:22.550 --> 00:29:24.310
(I'm here. See you soon.)

00:29:44.070 --> 00:29:45.350
(I'll wait for you at the restaurant.)

00:29:59.480 --> 00:30:00.510
Will you catch a cold?

00:30:00.790 --> 00:30:02.350
Should I get you
some Ban Lan Gen or something?

00:30:02.590 --> 00:30:04.200
I'm fine. It's nothing serious.

00:30:04.830 --> 00:30:05.670
No need.

00:30:07.400 --> 00:30:08.720
How about I get some food?

00:30:08.720 --> 00:30:09.830
Eat early, sleep early.

00:30:09.830 --> 00:30:11.070
Aren't we going out tomorrow?

00:30:12.070 --> 00:30:13.440
We can eat together then.

00:30:19.110 --> 00:30:20.830
You've been running around all night.

00:30:20.890 --> 00:30:21.750
Rest early.

00:30:21.750 --> 00:30:22.680
Wait for me, I'll be quick.

00:30:22.680 --> 00:30:23.520
Okay?

00:30:26.750 --> 00:30:27.590
Hey.

00:30:48.120 --> 00:30:49.590
One casserole porridge to go, please.

00:30:49.590 --> 00:30:51.510
Sir, it might take a while.

00:30:51.510 --> 00:30:52.350
That's fine.

00:30:52.370 --> 00:30:53.400
Alright, please wait.

00:30:54.260 --> 00:30:55.100
Hello.

00:30:57.270 --> 00:30:58.960
I came as soon as I got your message.

00:30:59.750 --> 00:31:00.590
So…

00:31:01.140 --> 00:31:02.270
What are you doing tomorrow?

00:31:02.750 --> 00:31:04.400
Let's walk along the riverbank tomorrow.

00:31:06.400 --> 00:31:07.960
I can't tomorrow. I have to...

00:31:08.550 --> 00:31:09.400
stay with her.

00:31:09.780 --> 00:31:11.550
Then let's grab some dessert
tomorrow night.

00:31:12.380 --> 00:31:13.550
There's a great place nearby.

00:31:13.830 --> 00:31:14.670
I'm sorry.

00:31:16.000 --> 00:31:16.840
I feel like…

00:31:17.300 --> 00:31:18.880
we should stick to what we said before.

00:31:19.750 --> 00:31:21.790
Maybe rethink where we stand.

00:31:26.750 --> 00:31:27.590
You and I…

00:31:29.070 --> 00:31:29.920
What relationship?

00:31:35.110 --> 00:31:36.200
I dropped my rehearsal.

00:31:36.480 --> 00:31:38.030
Came here just because of your message.

00:31:38.440 --> 00:31:39.790
And this is all you wanted to say?

00:31:41.240 --> 00:31:42.640
I honestly didn't know you'd come.

00:31:45.000 --> 00:31:45.840
It's alright.

00:31:46.640 --> 00:31:47.720
I'm just glad you're okay.

00:31:48.880 --> 00:31:50.640
I'll take this as a day off for myself.

00:31:51.350 --> 00:31:52.640
Rehearsals have been exhausting.

00:31:55.250 --> 00:31:56.920
Don't forget to
come to the official performance.

00:32:00.790 --> 00:32:01.630
I won't.

00:32:24.680 --> 00:32:25.550
Hurry to her?

00:32:26.880 --> 00:32:28.200
Yeah, Yu's waiting.

00:32:28.550 --> 00:32:29.390
Hey.

00:32:30.310 --> 00:32:31.640
That girl just now.

00:32:33.790 --> 00:32:34.630
What are you trying to do?

00:32:36.270 --> 00:32:37.240
Your schedule

00:32:37.240 --> 00:32:38.270
is packed.

00:32:40.200 --> 00:32:41.160
Famous musician.

00:32:41.680 --> 00:32:42.920
Next time you hold a concert.

00:32:43.640 --> 00:32:44.590
Save me a ticket.

00:32:52.310 --> 00:32:53.750
Yu, it's me.

00:32:55.200 --> 00:32:56.160
I'm at the restaurant.

00:32:57.000 --> 00:32:58.440
You and Xiu both caught a chill.

00:32:59.000 --> 00:33:00.480
I'll pack some porridge and bring it up.

00:33:01.830 --> 00:33:03.680
No need, Xiu went downstairs to buy it.

00:33:04.880 --> 00:33:06.590
I think I saw Xiu in the restaurant.

00:33:07.510 --> 00:33:08.350
Yes.

00:33:09.480 --> 00:33:10.480
Thanks, Hua.

00:33:10.640 --> 00:33:11.480
It's nothing.

00:33:11.920 --> 00:33:12.760
Rest well.

00:33:17.930 --> 00:33:18.960
What are you really up to?

00:33:20.750 --> 00:33:22.640
I think Yu has the right to know

00:33:23.030 --> 00:33:24.750
how busy you are outside.

00:33:25.480 --> 00:33:26.880
Bro, she's married.

00:33:26.880 --> 00:33:27.960
And you're married too.

00:33:29.200 --> 00:33:30.040
Mm?

00:33:32.790 --> 00:33:34.070
Yu has her own achievements

00:33:34.750 --> 00:33:35.750
and her own pride.

00:33:36.200 --> 00:33:37.040
Her career's going well.

00:33:37.640 --> 00:33:38.480
She and you…

00:33:39.270 --> 00:33:40.510
Plus your group of friends…

00:33:41.110 --> 00:33:42.270
You're from different worlds.

00:33:44.400 --> 00:33:45.640
I hope you, the famous musician,

00:33:45.830 --> 00:33:47.350
as you chase your dream,

00:33:47.350 --> 00:33:48.510
stops and asks yourself

00:33:49.070 --> 00:33:50.680
who actually puts food on your table.

00:33:58.200 --> 00:33:59.110
Don't be afraid.

00:34:00.750 --> 00:34:02.480
I won't tell Yu
about what just happened.

00:34:03.790 --> 00:34:04.630
Mm.

00:34:07.110 --> 00:34:08.280
At least not for now.

00:34:25.710 --> 00:34:26.550
Why don't you wear it?

00:34:29.190 --> 00:34:30.440
I've never really worn a ring.

00:34:30.760 --> 00:34:31.710
I'm just not used to it.

00:34:31.710 --> 00:34:33.190
Afraid I'll lose it
if I take it off and on.

00:34:33.760 --> 00:34:34.710
Then we...

00:34:35.000 --> 00:34:36.280
Turn it into a necklace or something?

00:34:38.030 --> 00:34:39.670
But I still prefer the one you gave me.

00:34:44.550 --> 00:34:45.390
Mm.

00:34:46.230 --> 00:34:47.670
The signature dish is really good.

00:34:48.190 --> 00:34:49.290
- Try it.
- Mm.

00:34:58.280 --> 00:34:59.150
Eat slowly.

00:34:59.590 --> 00:35:00.510
It's got a fresh taste.

00:35:08.070 --> 00:35:08.910
Don't move.

00:35:13.670 --> 00:35:14.800
Why'd you

00:35:15.510 --> 00:35:16.550
get me a razor?

00:35:18.070 --> 00:35:20.280
Your old one's been used for years.

00:35:21.150 --> 00:35:23.440
I was thinking of
getting you an electric one,

00:35:23.710 --> 00:35:24.550
but then I thought

00:35:24.550 --> 00:35:26.360
you're probably used to the manual kind.

00:35:29.800 --> 00:35:31.000
Okay.

00:35:31.710 --> 00:35:33.630
Can I keep using the one you gave me?

00:35:35.150 --> 00:35:36.670
Yeah. I checked the material.

00:35:36.670 --> 00:35:37.800
It'll last ages.

00:35:40.230 --> 00:35:42.280
You have a tiny mole here.

00:35:42.510 --> 00:35:43.670
Really tiny.

00:35:45.440 --> 00:35:46.400
You just noticed that?

00:35:49.920 --> 00:35:51.840
Your eyebrows are so thick.

00:35:56.480 --> 00:35:58.550
Never realized
your nose is this straight.

00:36:04.230 --> 00:36:05.880
Someone once told me,

00:36:06.880 --> 00:36:08.280
being together

00:36:08.760 --> 00:36:09.880
means turning each other into

00:36:09.880 --> 00:36:11.400
someone you don't like.

00:36:13.800 --> 00:36:14.640
Let me see you.

00:36:17.960 --> 00:36:18.800
Have you changed?

00:36:21.590 --> 00:36:23.000
Seeing you this close,

00:36:24.030 --> 00:36:25.840
I can spot every tiny flaw.

00:36:27.630 --> 00:36:28.470
So,

00:36:28.960 --> 00:36:29.880
do you dislike me now?

00:36:33.800 --> 00:36:34.710
The pores.

00:36:36.400 --> 00:36:37.440
The little moles.

00:36:39.280 --> 00:36:40.320
The spots.

00:36:41.800 --> 00:36:43.030
The fine lines.

00:36:45.510 --> 00:36:47.590
This is the real you.

00:36:50.920 --> 00:36:51.760
And me?

00:36:55.550 --> 00:36:56.550
Have I changed?

00:36:58.230 --> 00:37:00.880
You're a bit different from
what I thought.

00:37:03.000 --> 00:37:04.070
How so?

00:37:06.030 --> 00:37:07.510
I never imagined

00:37:08.510 --> 00:37:10.440
you'd love all these
weird things,

00:37:10.440 --> 00:37:11.280
leaving them

00:37:11.510 --> 00:37:13.400
all over the house.

00:37:16.320 --> 00:37:17.670
You starting to hate me?

00:37:19.670 --> 00:37:20.760
I just feel like

00:37:21.590 --> 00:37:22.880
the house got smaller,

00:37:24.150 --> 00:37:25.360
only big enough for you and me.

00:37:26.280 --> 00:37:27.120
But

00:37:27.920 --> 00:37:28.760
it's nice.

00:37:28.960 --> 00:37:29.920
So be it.

00:37:29.920 --> 00:37:31.510
Can't you say something sweet?

00:37:46.550 --> 00:37:47.800
Let me trim your eyebrows, okay?

00:37:48.670 --> 00:37:50.280
Trim my eyebrows? No way.

00:37:50.440 --> 00:37:51.280
No trimming.

00:37:52.590 --> 00:37:54.030
Trust me, after trimming,

00:37:54.030 --> 00:37:55.110
- you'll feel great.
- No.

00:37:55.110 --> 00:37:55.950
I said no.

00:37:56.410 --> 00:37:57.510
I'll pick you up after work.

00:37:57.710 --> 00:37:59.400
Let's eat Western food, okay?

00:37:59.840 --> 00:38:00.680
Mm, okay.

00:38:01.050 --> 00:38:02.590
I was actually thinking about hot pot.

00:38:03.000 --> 00:38:03.840
Hot pot?

00:38:04.320 --> 00:38:05.230
Hot pot works too.

00:38:05.960 --> 00:38:07.150
Don't always go along with me.

00:38:07.840 --> 00:38:08.960
Or you'll get tired.

00:38:08.960 --> 00:38:10.150
Don't you always go along with me?

00:38:11.710 --> 00:38:12.550
Do I?

00:38:13.000 --> 00:38:13.840
Yeah.

00:38:16.400 --> 00:38:17.240
How about this.

00:38:17.880 --> 00:38:18.960
Let's decide it with this.

00:38:19.630 --> 00:38:21.400
Heads for Western food,
tails for hot pot.

00:38:21.400 --> 00:38:22.240
Fair enough?

00:38:25.710 --> 00:38:26.960
Western food. It's settled.

00:38:26.960 --> 00:38:27.880
Best two out of three.

00:38:28.420 --> 00:38:29.280
Come on.

00:38:29.280 --> 00:38:31.190
Director Sen, time to head to work.

00:38:31.190 --> 00:38:33.030
Otherwise,
how will you afford to keep me?

00:38:33.030 --> 00:38:33.920
Mm?

00:38:33.920 --> 00:38:34.760
Alright.

00:38:35.650 --> 00:38:36.760
I'll pick you up after work.

00:38:36.760 --> 00:38:37.670
- Go on.
- Okay.

00:38:37.670 --> 00:38:38.510
- Bye bye.
- Bye bye.

00:38:44.400 --> 00:38:45.360
Boss.

00:38:45.360 --> 00:38:47.030
The wedding photos
from yesterday are polished.

00:38:47.280 --> 00:38:48.120
Mm.

00:38:48.220 --> 00:38:49.070
The client asked

00:38:49.070 --> 00:38:51.000
if we can add two extra 40-inch prints.

00:38:51.230 --> 00:38:52.070
What do you think?

00:38:52.360 --> 00:38:53.200
Sure.

00:38:53.480 --> 00:38:54.750
The shots turned out well.

00:38:54.750 --> 00:38:55.630
Okay.

00:38:55.630 --> 00:38:57.710
Pick one to blow up

00:38:57.710 --> 00:38:58.960
for our window display.

00:38:59.840 --> 00:39:01.710
Their looks are average.

00:39:02.030 --> 00:39:03.800
Might not grab much attention.

00:39:04.840 --> 00:39:05.680
Really?

00:39:07.110 --> 00:39:08.150
I think it's fine.

00:39:09.480 --> 00:39:10.920
You're just biased because it's him.

00:39:11.660 --> 00:39:12.510
Of course.

00:39:12.510 --> 00:39:14.440
Lun's photography skills are top-notch.

00:39:14.490 --> 00:39:15.590
What nonsense are you talking?

00:39:17.400 --> 00:39:18.400
Sorry, Boss.

00:39:19.110 --> 00:39:20.880
I… I didn't mean anything.

00:39:21.440 --> 00:39:23.150
It's fine. You can leave now.

00:39:23.150 --> 00:39:23.990
Okay.

00:39:26.050 --> 00:39:27.440
Luanluan's stage play is on tonight.

00:39:27.880 --> 00:39:29.400
I'll leave early to pick you up.

00:39:29.400 --> 00:39:30.510
We can eat nearby.

00:39:31.630 --> 00:39:33.150
Oh right, I forgot to tell you.

00:39:33.760 --> 00:39:35.510
Luanluan gave me the stage play tickets.

00:39:36.210 --> 00:39:37.510
No wonder she didn't give me any.

00:39:38.510 --> 00:39:39.510
Also,

00:39:39.510 --> 00:39:40.800
Yu treated me to meal the other day,

00:39:41.150 --> 00:39:42.880
and gave me two sets of clothes.

00:39:45.150 --> 00:39:45.990
Actually,

00:39:46.480 --> 00:39:47.440
Yu

00:39:48.280 --> 00:39:49.120
is a good person.

00:39:52.960 --> 00:39:54.360
But I really don't like

00:39:54.360 --> 00:39:56.550
being around both of them
at the same time.

00:39:59.280 --> 00:40:00.120
I get it.

00:40:02.920 --> 00:40:03.840
About that photo,

00:40:04.010 --> 00:40:04.960
you actually could've...

00:40:04.960 --> 00:40:06.510
I didn't send that photo to Yu.

00:40:08.110 --> 00:40:09.440
Xiu's your close friend.

00:40:09.440 --> 00:40:11.440
I understand
you're speaking from your friend's side.

00:40:13.960 --> 00:40:15.710
But I really...

00:40:16.030 --> 00:40:17.800
It's really hard to
pretend nothing's wrong

00:40:17.800 --> 00:40:19.670
watching him with Luanluan.

00:40:21.150 --> 00:40:22.230
I have my own stance.

00:40:23.630 --> 00:40:24.470
I get it.

00:40:26.770 --> 00:40:28.400
But there's something
I haven't told you yet.

00:40:30.880 --> 00:40:31.720
Xiu

00:40:31.880 --> 00:40:33.070
is gonna end things with Luanluan.

00:40:33.800 --> 00:40:34.640
End things?

00:40:35.920 --> 00:40:37.190
How?

00:40:38.110 --> 00:40:39.070
I have no idea.

00:40:40.440 --> 00:40:41.920
But you can tell

00:40:42.710 --> 00:40:44.190
Yu already knows about them, right?

00:40:45.320 --> 00:40:46.320
But even now,

00:40:46.320 --> 00:40:47.480
she still hasn't left Xiu.

00:40:48.070 --> 00:40:49.880
That means she has her reasons.

00:40:51.150 --> 00:40:52.030
And they've been together

00:40:52.030 --> 00:40:53.190
for so many years.

00:40:54.320 --> 00:40:56.030
For so many years.

00:40:57.110 --> 00:40:58.000
Feelings

00:40:58.000 --> 00:40:59.840
can't be explained in just a few words.

00:41:01.920 --> 00:41:04.280
So in the end, the choice is up to Yu.

00:41:04.960 --> 00:41:05.800
Yeah.

00:41:07.110 --> 00:41:08.190
Only Yu knows

00:41:09.280 --> 00:41:10.280
what it feels like.

00:41:14.190 --> 00:41:15.480
You want to let them be together?

00:41:16.150 --> 00:41:16.990
No.

00:41:17.550 --> 00:41:19.110
I want to do this for myself.

00:41:19.920 --> 00:41:21.150
I'm soft-hearted

00:41:21.630 --> 00:41:22.590
and nostalgic.

00:41:23.280 --> 00:41:24.840
I'm scared if he cries and begs me,

00:41:24.840 --> 00:41:26.320
I'll forgive him.

00:41:27.590 --> 00:41:28.960
So I wanna see

00:41:29.800 --> 00:41:31.360
them madly in love,

00:41:31.880 --> 00:41:33.070
unable to bear being apart.

00:41:33.670 --> 00:41:35.800
That would give me
the resolve to let go.

00:41:37.400 --> 00:41:39.590
You're really gonna
hold on till the end?

00:41:40.590 --> 00:41:41.590
I guess so.

00:41:42.710 --> 00:41:43.710
Either someone leaves or

00:41:44.920 --> 00:41:46.550
your heart goes numb
before you can move on.

00:41:54.710 --> 00:41:55.880
Pick me up early after work.

00:41:56.070 --> 00:41:57.000
Okay, see you tonight.

00:41:57.280 --> 00:41:58.550
- Bye bye.
- Bye bye.

00:42:18.710 --> 00:42:21.360
(Chen Qing)
(Dr. Lin, sorry. I can't meet today.)

00:42:25.630 --> 00:42:27.150
(Okay, let's contact tomorrow.)

