♪I'll admit♪

00:42:37.480 --> 00:42:41.519
♪My back is faced against the wall♪

00:42:42.400 --> 00:42:46.266
♪There's nothing that
I wouldn't try to do♪

00:42:46.291 --> 00:42:50.479
♪For this feeling to have you♪

00:42:50.760 --> 00:42:52.959
♪I'll resist♪

00:42:53.280 --> 00:42:55.294
♪Your gaze, your lips♪

00:42:55.319 --> 00:42:57.479
♪Your touches again♪

00:42:58.360 --> 00:43:02.340
♪There's no one that
I wouldn't try to fool♪

00:43:02.365 --> 00:43:05.399
♪For an image of you♪

00:43:06.400 --> 00:43:08.839
♪Take my hand again♪

00:43:08.840 --> 00:43:10.599
♪Take my mind again♪

00:43:10.680 --> 00:43:14.039
♪Break into my heart again♪

00:43:14.440 --> 00:43:16.617
♪I'm falling out again♪

00:43:16.642 --> 00:43:18.479
♪I'm on my knees again♪

00:43:18.480 --> 00:43:22.319
♪To beg for the truth♪

00:43:24.160 --> 00:43:28.319
♪Tell me the secret of love♪

00:43:28.320 --> 00:43:33.319
♪Is that the secret to love♪

00:43:33.680 --> 00:43:36.639
♪I thought it had came from
below us♪

00:43:36.720 --> 00:43:40.119
♪Did it come from above♪

00:43:40.200 --> 00:43:43.959
♪Tell me the secret of love♪

00:43:44.200 --> 00:43:49.279
♪Is that the secret to love♪

00:43:49.680 --> 00:43:52.119
♪Is it violent or warming, entrancing♪

00:43:52.120 --> 00:43:56.559
♪This secret of love♪